{"id": "1266639999143641100", "channel_id": "1266254397680386139", "type": 0, "author_id": "676337286769672192", "author_name": "hailananxie7110", "author_bot": false, "content": "除非運氣很好，鏽蝕鋼鋸有買到，白銀造物真的太多了，要買的指定的白銀，比咒物都難啊...", "timestamp": "2024-07-27T06:15:08.829000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1266254397680386139", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "超限版本下，純血肉隊伍的理論組成猜想", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1260133992636743681", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1266640639907467266", "channel_id": "1266254397680386139", "type": 0, "author_id": "676337286769672192", "author_name": "hailananxie7110", "author_bot": false, "content": "已經跟貓建議三次有了吧，弄個造物天賦，或是造物研究所(神父劇情裡有)，雷打不動的堅決不改XD", "timestamp": "2024-07-27T06:17:41.599000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1266254397680386139", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "超限版本下，純血肉隊伍的理論組成猜想", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1260133992636743681", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1266809023533944842", "channel_id": "1266809023533944842", "type": 0, "author_id": "690870717910351902", "author_name": "akaashi1205", "author_bot": false, "content": "因為不知道發在哪裡所以在這裡發貼了，如果違規了我馬上刪🥹\n\n0氪咸魚，開服從開始就沒有看過任何攻略就盲沖，無什麼腦子，活動全靠大佬助戰。一直都是存圖鑑而已，但是打關卡好痛苦，最近想好好培養一下角色，但是沒什麼思路。想問一下各位大佬，在不PVP的前提下，想通關主線（現在到第七章頭）同融災可以求教一下組隊思路嗎？<:wish:1236951537788649492> <:wish:1236951537788649492> <:wish:1236951537788649492>\n\n我自己平時用的隊（組隊全憑感覺\n混沌： 朵拉莉莉24\n血肉：神父索蕾爾24莉莉/朵/拉\n超維：艾瑞卡24莉莉朵 （以前用的是艾瑞卡+汀克特夫人旺達亂配）\n觸手：圖魯希萊斯特里菲24\n\n有什麼不妥求輕噴🥹", "timestamp": "2024-07-27T17:26:47.384000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1266809024075137076", "filename": "IMG_20240728_010055.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 191108, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1266809023533944842/1266809024075137076/IMG_20240728_010055.jpg?ex=69cc03d7&is=69cab257&hm=336376e6a339ea34cba5ee3ebd7c55de23d76e66071b8783ecf489bcf5d8a5d0&"}, {"id": "1266809024507154604", "filename": "IMG_20240728_010251.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 199728, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1266809023533944842/1266809024507154604/IMG_20240728_010251.jpg?ex=69cc03d7&is=69cab257&hm=5480a49e2ade6b33cf2693e0025436a662f6a29e80863c8847fd238d9a95cb20&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1266809023533944842", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "咸魚玩家求教", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
