{"id": "1266841551905099969", "channel_id": "1266809023533944842", "type": 19, "author_id": "690870717910351902", "author_name": "akaashi1205", "author_bot": false, "content": "好的不好意思🥹 謝謝解答", "timestamp": "2024-07-27T19:36:02.752000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["771169877121564703"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1266809935241547786", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1266809023533944842", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "咸魚玩家求教", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1266842564112158763", "channel_id": "1266809023533944842", "type": 19, "author_id": "690870717910351902", "author_name": "akaashi1205", "author_bot": false, "content": "謝謝，但是請問溫多是指旺達嗎？🥹", "timestamp": "2024-07-27T19:40:04.081000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1137328302135181312"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1266812720657727530", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1266809023533944842", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "咸魚玩家求教", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1266849250856140924", "channel_id": "1266809023533944842", "type": 0, "author_id": "676337286769672192", "author_name": "hailananxie7110", "author_bot": false, "content": "依照你朵爾的深化，至少是5個多月的號了，角色等級跟啟靈情況不大正常，先行分配資源，再考慮怎麼打吧。\n個人是推薦24+拉、朵、奧，這樣就能很穩了。\n靈核明面上是7顆，應該是沒甚麼在打災區，可考慮打個300意思意思一下，優先給主力隊伍需要數值的角色，朵爾不值得，真愛另話。\n\n下個月快到了，沉澱商店的母版跟視界記得買，建議優先投入：24，3啟；羊媽至少2；神父。", "timestamp": "2024-07-27T20:06:38.325000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1266809023533944842", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "咸魚玩家求教", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1266849881436192908", "channel_id": "1266809023533944842", "type": 0, "author_id": "676337286769672192", "author_name": "hailananxie7110", "author_bot": false, "content": "送的三界域角色，最好都3啟(每天900，每個月夠買3碎片了)，算是該界域的基礎角色吧，免費的+-養，尤其是艾繼絲，不虧的，輔助性質極強。", "timestamp": "2024-07-27T20:09:08.667000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1266809023533944842", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "咸魚玩家求教", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1266850629582585957", "channel_id": "1266809023533944842", "type": 0, "author_id": "676337286769672192", "author_name": "hailananxie7110", "author_bot": false, "content": "調查商店的每月3X2片，建議都買，其實四小強都不錯的。", "timestamp": "2024-07-27T20:12:07.039000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1266809023533944842", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "咸魚玩家求教", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1266853219405922305", "channel_id": "1266809023533944842", "type": 0, "author_id": "676337286769672192", "author_name": "hailananxie7110", "author_bot": false, "content": "災區隊伍推薦：\n1.艾瑞卡、莉茲、寧菲亞、珈倫。\n2.希洛、菲因特、羅坦、艾爾瓦。\n3.羊媽、神父、朵爾、莉莉。\n4.拉蒙娜、24、奧吉爾、潘迪亞。\n5.圖魯、墨菲、米粒、大腿24。\n\n...商店有的碎片，命輪，還是建議能搬就搬，效用、強度可能都沒有抽的好，但PVE還是夠用的。\n\n末 祝遊戲愉快😆", "timestamp": "2024-07-27T20:22:24.501000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1266809023533944842", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "咸魚玩家求教", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
